{
  "storyId": "oregon_trail_demo_v2",
  "title": "Oregon Trail",
  "startSectionId": "OT1",
  "save": {
    "defaults": {
      "sectionId": "OT1",
      "stats": { "W": 2, "E": 2, "A": 2, "L": 2, "T": 2, "H": 2 },
      "resources": { "HP": 10, "REPUTATION": 0 },
      "progress": { "level": 1, "xp": 0 },
      "flags": { "river_scouted": false },
      "inventory": {
        "consumables": ["healing_salve"],
        "weapons": ["rusty_dagger"],
        "armors": ["leather_jerkin"],
        "specialItems": ["candle"]
      },
      "equipped": { "weapon": "rusty_dagger", "armor": "leather_jerkin", "special": "candle" }
    }
  },
  "sections": [
    {
      "id": "OT1",
      "text": [
        "The trail is a long sentence with no punctuation.",
        "By midday, you reach a river that doesn’t look impressed by wagons.",
        { "__sys": true, "tier": "whisper", "text": "Demo hook: a classic river crossing—risk, clarity, and fair HP penalties." }
      ],
      "choices": [
        { "id": "OT1_SCOUT", "text": "Scout for a shallow crossing.", "to": "OT2" },
        { "id": "OT1_PUSH", "text": "Cross immediately (save time, risk damage).", "to": "OT3" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "OT2",
      "text": [
        "You walk the bank, eyes on the current, ears on your own doubt.",
        "You find a shallow bend—still dangerous, but negotiable."
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "OT2_MARK",
          "text": "Mark the spot and return to the wagon.",
          "to": "OT4",
          "onChoose": [
            { "op": "SET_FLAG", "key": "river_scouted", "value": true },
            { "op": "APPEND_TEXT", "lines": [{ "__sys": true, "tier": "whisper", "text": "You learned something. Risk goes down." }] }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "OT3",
      "text": [
        "You urge the wagon forward. The river answers immediately.",
        "Cold water slaps the wheels and tries to take a vote.",
        { "__sys": true, "tier": "explicit", "text": "Reckless crossings can cost HP. Here, it’s small but real." }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "OT3_TAKE",
          "text": "Fight through the current.",
          "to": "OT5",
          "onChoose": [
            { "op": "ADD_RESOURCE", "resource": "HP", "amount": -2 },
            { "op": "APPEND_TEXT", "lines": [{ "__sys": true, "tier": "neutral", "text": "HP -2." }] }
          ]
        },
        { "id": "OT3_BACK", "text": "Back off and scout first.", "to": "OT2" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "OT4",
      "text": [
        "You line the wagon up at the shallow bend.",
        "The river still wants trouble, but you’re not offering as much."
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "OT4_CROSS",
          "text": "Cross at the shallow bend.",
          "to": "OT5",
          "onChoose": [
            { "op": "APPEND_TEXT", "lines": [{ "__sys": true, "tier": "whisper", "text": "Good call. The risk was managed." }] }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "OT5",
      "text": [
        "On the far bank, you take inventory of what survived: wagon, supplies, pride.",
        { "__sys": true, "tier": "neutral", "text": "Oregon Trail demo stub complete. Next: expand choices, hazards, and longer run." }
      ],
      "choices": [
        { "id": "OT5_MENU", "text": "Return to Main Menu.", "to": "MENU" }
      ]
    }
  ]
}